data.meta_description: PAWS helps cats, dogs and wild animals get the critical care they need to go home and thrive.
data.text:
PAWS Wildlife Center has moved to 13508 State Route 9 SE in Snohomish.

If you need help with a wild animal, use our online self-service or call 425-412-4040.

Online Wildlife Self-Service

America's Favorite Pet

PAWS is the nonprofit beneficiary of funds raised by Colossal through the America’s Favorite Pet Competition. Colossal is a nationally registered professional fundraiser and the global leader in modern giving with a mission to inspire people to advocate for themselves and those in need. America’s Favorite Pet offers participants the opportunity to make their mark while also making a big impact. We are grateful for their generous support.
